# Prompt para Antgravity Design Mode (Gemini 3.0)

I am writing a prompt to use in Antgravity Design Mode: an AI agent specialized in designing beautiful landing pages powered by Gemini 3.0. In addition to React/Shadcn/Tailwind code generation, this agent can also generate images, short videos and get stock photos from the internet.

## IMPORTANT: Mobile First Approach

This landing page MUST be designed with a **mobile-first approach**. All styles should start from mobile and scale up to desktop using responsive breakpoints (sm, md, lg, xl). The majority of traffic will come from WhatsApp, so mobile experience is critical.

## Assets

All images will be provided via upload:
- **Background Hero:** `bg-campo-grande.jpg` - Photo of "CAMPO GRANDE" landmark with yellow ip√™ tree
- **Logo:** `logo-jotta.png` - "Jotta de Autoescolas" logo (red text, transparent background)

Do not generate or search for these specific assets. Use the uploaded files.

