## Color Palette

| Name | Hex | Usage |
|------|-----|-------|
| Red Primary | #DC2626 | CTAs, highlights, borders |
| Red Light | #EF4444 | Text emphasis |
| Green Primary | #22C55E | Form CTA, WhatsApp, success |
| Green Light | #4ADE80 | Text highlights |
| Yellow | #FBBF24 | Alert emphasis |
| Dark BG | #111827 | Section backgrounds |
| Gray 800 | #1F2937 | Cards, timer boxes |
| Gray 700 | #374151 | Borders |
| Gray 400 | #9CA3AF | Secondary text |
| Gray 200 | #E5E7EB | Body text on dark |
| White | #FFFFFF | Primary text, form bg |

---

## Typography

- **Headings:** System font stack, font-black (900)
- **Body:** System font stack, font-normal (400)
- **Responsive scale:** Use clamp() or Tailwind responsive prefixes

---

## Design Principles

1. **Mobile First:** All styles start mobile, scale up
2. **High Contrast:** Dark backgrounds, bright CTAs
3. **Urgency:** Countdown, limited slots messaging
4. **Trust:** Clear differentials, local addresses
5. **Conversion Focus:** Form always visible, multiple CTAs

---

## Responsive Breakpoints (Tailwind)

- `sm`: 640px
- `md`: 768px  
- `lg`: 1024px (2-column layout starts here)
- `xl`: 1280px

---

Please generate the complete React/Tailwind code following these specifications exactly. Ensure all mobile-first responsive classes are properly applied.